actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Public Works.

official_title: A bill to provide that the reservoir formed by the lock and dam referred to as the "Jones Bluff lock and dam" on the Alabama River, Ala., shall hereafter be known as the "Robert F. Henry lock and dam."

summary.text: Provides that the reservoir formed by the lock and dam referred to as the "Jones Bluff lock and dam" on the Alabama River, Alabama, shall hereafter be known as the Robert F. Henry lock and dam.
